item.title: How to get cache to load for webclient?
item.dc:creator: @Nuke207 Nuke207
item.description:
@Nuke207 wrote:

Ok for HTML:

<html>
<title>Webclient</title>
<center><applet name="app" width="765" height="503" 
archive="JAR URL" code="client">
</applet></center>
</html>

replace the title part with what you want as the page title and jar url is a link to the uploaded jar(thats the client made into a jar and signed )
